data.description: Welcome to this delightful move-in-ready home located in the heart of Marshall. Spanning an impressive 1,969 sqft, this home features 4 generously sized bedrooms and 2 full well-appointed bathrooms, making it an ideal choice for anyone seeking ample living space. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a large main level living area that provides a welcoming atmosphere for both relaxation and entertainment. The recent updates are evident throughout, showcasing a newer roof and windows that enhance the home's efficiency and appeal. The interior has been freshly painted, and newer flooring has been laid down, adding a fresh and contemporary feel to the home. The heart of this residence, the kitchen, has been completely revitalized with new countertops, cabinets, and includes all the necessary appliances. Adjacent to the kitchen, you'll find a convenient laundry area, further emphasizing the home's focus on practical living. Situated in a friendly and vibrant community in the City of Marshall, this property enjoys a great location that combines a peaceful residential atmosphere with easy access to local amenities. This house represents a fantastic opportunity for those desiring a ready-to-move-in home that balances style, comfort, and practicality. Don't miss out on making this lovely Marshall residence your new home. Contact Clint for your private showing today! 269-317-0127
